highlights.text: Justin Bieber has the most spots on Top Songs Imphal. “Ghost” is the highest at #6.
“Guru-Gee (Nang Ngei I Ni)” by Hope Music is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Imphal, up 30 spots at #17.
“Dandelions” by Ruth B. has been on Top Songs Imphal the longest, at 51 weeks straight.
“Unholy (feat. Kim Petras)” by Sam Smith and Kim Petras is the highest new entry on Top Songs Imphal at #63.
